trans-unit.source: Represents the enumerator for <see cref="T:System.Management.MethodData" /> objects in the <see cref="T:System.Management.MethodDataCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: Rappresenta l'enumeratore per gli oggetti <see cref="T:System.Management.MethodData" /> nella raccolta <see cref="T:System.Management.MethodDataCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: The following example enumerates through the methods in the **Win32_LogicalDisk** class and displays them.

trans-unit.source: Returns the current <see cref="T:System.Management.MethodData" /> in the <see cref="T:System.Management.MethodDataCollection" /> enumeration.
